<p>The <code>PaginationListItem</code> is one rung in the
  pagination list. Pass <code>ellipsis: true</code> for a
  non-interactive gap marker (the macro sets
  <code>data-variant="ellipsis"</code> and
  <code>aria-hidden="true"</code>). See the
  <a href="/components/pagination-nav/">PaginationNav demo</a> for
  the composed example.</p>
